title: Branch numbers of Banco Santander globally 2012 to 2019
summary: Overall Number of branches has increased over the Year.
Number of branches is roughly constant from 2014 to 2015, slightly increasing from 2015 to 2017, and finally slightly decreasing from 2017 to 2018.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year 2016 and 2017.
The highest Number of branches, of value 13697.0 was reached at Year 2017
The lowest Number of branches, of value 12235.0 was reported at Year 2016
